Class MediaGroup

java.lang.Object
com.apptasticsoftware.rssreader.module.mediarss.MetadataImpl
com.apptasticsoftware.rssreader.module.mediarss.MediaGroup
All Implemented Interfaces:
Metadata
public class MediaGroup extends MetadataImpl
A group element that allows grouping of <media:content> elements that are effectively the same content, yet different representations. For instance: the same song recorded in both WAV and MP3 format.

Example: <media:group> <media:content url="http://www.foo.com/song.wav" type="audio/wav" bitrate="128" isDefault="true" /> <p> <media:content url="http://www.foo.com/song.mp3" type="audio/mpeg" bitrate="64" /> </media:group>
